ed against actual codebase state |\n| Current Block State | HIGH | All 14 CONCERNS.md locations traced to current code |\n\n### Open Questions\n1. Whether to keep `client.app?.log?.()` or switch to `console.warn` — SPEC requires `console.warn`, follow SPEC\n2. Where to place the Zod schema for SdkMessageShape — the agent's Discretion (inline vs separate file)\n3. Which allowedKeys for create-governance-session — start with same 5 keys as buildMinimalEnv\n\n### Ready for Planning\nResearch complete. Planner can now create PLAN.md files for 4 independent tasks (REQ-01 through REQ-04).",
